11 An Act relating to firefighters; prohibiting certain
mandatory volunteer or rural firefighter training;
12 providing for codification; and providing an
effective date.
13
14
15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
17 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 325.5 of Title 74, unless there
18 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
19 No volunteer or rural firefighter shall be required to attend
20 any state or county mandatory training.
21 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
